objects.name: helpcommand
objects.string:
Here's the list of commands:

help - Shows this screen
open appName.nid - Opens an app (eg. NidBrowse.nid)
credits - Shows people helped with project
wifi del profile_name - Deletes selected wifi network
fl del <file/folder> - Deletes specified file
